00:09:14.769 --> 00:09:16.409
What do we mean?

00:09:16.409 --> 00:09:21.370
Well, if we put forth no effort, there's nothing for Jehovah to multiply.

00:09:21.370 --> 00:09:24.009
See, what is 10 times zero?

00:09:24.009 --> 00:09:25.009
Zero.

00:09:25.009 --> 00:09:30.970
A hundred times zero, a thousand times zero, a million times zero, we still have zero.

00:09:30.970 --> 00:09:36.370
So if we don't do anything, Jehovah has nothing to multiply.

00:09:36.370 --> 00:09:44.009
Galatian 5.22 tells us that peace is an aspect of the fruitage of the Holy Spirit.

00:09:44.009 --> 00:09:48.730
