00:09:48.730 --> 00:09:57.409
In fact, John 1426 describes the Holy Spirit as a helper, but that expression helper doesn't

00:09:57.409 --> 00:10:04.090
indicate it will miraculously do the job for us with no effort on our part.

00:10:04.090 --> 00:10:05.769
Illustrate this if we can.

00:10:05.769 --> 00:10:11.769
Imagine that you're working very hard to paint the outside of your house, and a good friend

00:10:11.769 --> 00:10:15.289
comes to help you, now you're painting together.

00:10:15.289 --> 00:10:21.250
But then you decide, I'll just go back in the house, and I'll just take it easy.

00:10:21.250 --> 00:10:24.490
Well how long will your friend keep painting?

00:10:24.490 --> 00:10:30.929
If he continued painting, he's no longer a helper, he's doing the job for you.

00:10:30.929 --> 00:10:38.409
Luke 1113 tells us that Jehovah will give Holy Spirit to those asking him for it.

00:10:38.409 --> 00:10:44.809
So if we ask for Holy Spirit and then do our very best to work in harmony with that helper,

00:10:44.809 --> 00:10:52.610
we will enjoy peace with God, and we will enjoy and promote harmony, unity, and good relations

00:10:52.610 --> 00:10:54.090
with others.

00:10:54.090 --> 00:11:00.850
And what a pleasure it is to associate with those who display peace, this important aspect

00:11:00.850 --> 00:11:04.250
of the Spirit's fruitage.

