00:11:15.929 --> 00:11:24.889
But when a parent cuddles him and soothes him with reassuring words, he calms down immediately.

00:11:24.889 --> 00:11:33.370
Well David, at Psalm 55, 16 through 18, said that when he was troubled, he called out to

